Package gw.api.web.producer.agencybill.distributionwizard

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgencyCycleDistAccountView
    AgencyCycleDistAccountView serves to associate a given Account with a list of dist items for display in the AgencyDistributionWizard.
    AgencyCycleDistChargeOwnerView
    AgencyCycleDistChargeOwnerView serves to associate a given ChargeOwner (TAccount) with a list of dist items for display in the AgencyDistributionWizard.
    AgencyCycleDistCollateralRequirementView
    AgencyCycleDistCollateralRequirementView serves to associate a given CollateralRequirement with a list of dist items for display in the AgencyDistributionWizard.
    AgencyCycleDistCollateralView
    AgencyCycleDistCollateralView serves to associate a given Collateral with a list of dist items for display in the AgencyDistributionWizard.
    AgencyCycleDistPolicyView
    The View (UI) class for PolicyPeriods for use in the Agency Distribution Wizard.
    AgencyCycleDistView
    The View (UI) class for Agency Cycle Distributions (both Payments and Promises).
